{"tid":2393834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國跨黨派國會議員 提名「香港民主運動」角逐今年諾貝爾和平獎","createTime":"2021-02-03T18:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T01:15:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"13aed182a426b3e6aa7939ba3a5c82d5a5813152","tid":2393834,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:36:38.000Z","msg":"美國一個由民主共和兩黨國會議員組成的團體，提名香港民主運動競逐今年諾貝爾和平獎。<br />\n<br />\n提名人包括五位參議員和四位眾議員，以國會及行政當局中國委員會（CECC）聯席主席、共和黨參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）和CECC主席、民主黨眾議員麥高文（Jim McGovern）為首。他們在周一截止提名期結束前致函挪威奧斯陸諾貝爾委員會主席，表示和平獎可讓1997年香港主權移交中國後力抗自由被侵蝕的人發聲。<br />\n<br />\n信中提到，「多位民主倡導者已在獄中，有些流亡海外，更多候審的人有被定罪判刑之虞......獎項可表揚他們那份已鼓舞世界的勇氣和決心。」<br />\n<br />\n議員建議提名所有自1997年以來推動香港人權民主的人競逐獎項，「我們希望諾貝爾委員會繼續照亮爭取和平和中國人權的人。我們認為香港民主運動今年值得嘉獎」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210204/UTMAIS4TRJG7DBB3E7URSM6YQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210204%2FUTMAIS4TRJG7DBB3E7URSM6YQQ%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjfno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=3598ef8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210204%2FUTMAIS4TRJG7DBB3E7URSM6YQQ%2F&h=254bb5c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210204/UTMAIS4TRJG7DBB3E7URSM6YQQ/</a>"},{"pid":"87d1e5d6633b9cb9b1f8e36f985bd84446e8dc34","tid":2393834,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ee5b1e3f5c8bd9c2c32307f50983f0f1dec482","tid":2393834,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"